# GSD Integration for Claude Code

This project uses GSD (Get Shit Done) framework. Available commands and conventions:

## Available Skills
- `@accessibility` - WCAG accessibility audit
- `@agent-browser` - Browser automation
- `@best-practices` - Security & quality audit
- `@code-optimizer` - Performance optimization
- `@core-web-vitals` - LCP/INP/CLS optimization
- `@debug-like-expert` - Deep debugging
- `@frontend-design` - UI/UX design
- `@lint` - Code linting
- `@review` - Code review
- `@test` - Test generation/execution

